HEADWORD: Exploder
<hw>Ex*plod"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
or that which explodes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who rejects an opinion or scheme with open
contempt.</def> <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

